`mech format`
===============================================================================

`mech format` formats Mech source and Mechdown documents.

1. Format source
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

```sh
mech format main.mec --out formatted
```

2. HTML output
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

```sh
mech format docs/index.mec --html --out docs-out
```

3. Stylesheets and shim
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

```sh
mech format docs/index.mec --html --stylesheet include/docs.css --shim include/docs.html
```
